improved_metadata.title: Prince Shopkings Blues
improved_metadata.description: A quirky and humorous song about the daily grind at Prince Shopkings, a print shop, highlighting the chaos and camaraderie between Nick and Mike. It captures the frustrations and humor of dealing with malfunctioning equipment and tight deadlines.
improved_metadata.key_lyrics: Prince Shopkings, jamming all day, Paper jams trace the blues away
